import { Dropdown } from 'rsuite'

const instance = (
    <ButtonToolbar>
      <Dropdown title="More...">
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="edit2" /> Edit
        </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="eye" /> View
        </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="trash" /> Delete
        </Dropdown.Item>
      </Dropdown>
  
      <Dropdown
        title="New"
        renderTitle={children => {
          return <Button appearance="primary">{children} </Button>;
        }}
      >
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="user" /> New User
        </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="group" /> New Group
        </Dropdown.Item>
      </Dropdown>
      <Dropdown
        renderTitle={() => {
          return <IconButton appearance="primary" icon={<Icon icon="plus" />} circle />;
        }}
      >
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="user" /> New User
        </Dropdown.Item>
        <Dropdown.Item>
          <Icon icon="group" /> New Group
        </Dropdown.Item>
      </Dropdown>
    </ButtonToolbar>
  );

  export default instance;
